{"tid":219972,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一夫多妻制根本就更適合社會","createTime":"2017-04-27T15:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T08:51:04.000Z","uid":18818,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4122644b50a6c004d25d2f5ee52a006c86b72da5","tid":219972,"uid":18818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"根據人口比例，<br />\n中產以上既男性社會精英只佔社會既幾個%<br />\n但係千千萬萬既港女都只以呢一小個池塘為目標<br />\n<br />\n一夫一妻制大大打擊左佢地既競爭<br />\n造成大量既失敗者，結果先至有今日咁多剩女出現<br />\n<br />\n一夫多妻制根本完美解決左呢個供求問題<br />\n只要個男養得起，有咩問題？<br />\n女人講到尾都係上岸最緊要姐<br />\n比有錢佬包，一父多妻制反而先係女人既真正保障<br />\n唔只大婆有得分，二奶三奶都有份<br />\n<br />\n港女幾時出黎爭取？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5888a6b80e5c43fdebddb89f56be37ffa9423d","tid":219972,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:18:08.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"d29bcf17e66d7eb9c2301ded0aa2bc6a3dcbb2dd","tid":219972,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"又好似真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bfe1700b80b9860ea6aac98f0944be65245e4d","tid":219972,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"所以我懷疑一夫一妻根本係班有錢佬自己諗出黎保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中出情婦後：<br />\n我唔同得你結婚架，我有老婆架喇...<br />\n如果早d識到你你話幾好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4343ca67e79f21ea5c223d8f03ddaf7c44e51ef2","tid":219972,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"就算法律改變左 我驚你都係無改變過"},{"pid":"18e2e784111c1c37c09a0dac38926e56307263c5","tid":219972,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"咪on9<br />\n一夫多妻制只會令女人更加集中晒係d 高質素的男人到，<br />\n即係本身質素唔高既男人會由有老婆變冇老婆<br />\n舉個例子，<br />\n如